==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Thunderstone
<hw>Thun"der*stone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
thunderbolt, -- formerly believed to be a stone.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Fear no more the lightning flash,⟦br⟧
Nor the all-dreaded <qex>thunderstone</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld> <def>A belemnite. See
<er>Belemnite</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thunderstorm</ent>⟦br⟧
